Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the Millennium Puzzle complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The young boy Yugi Mutou became a master of the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was challenged by a person that has a Millennium Item like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the owner of the Millennium Eye, Pegasus, and went to the Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save the soul of Sugoroku, that was stolen by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Together with his friends and with his other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(295,132)}Cut through the Darkness! Sealing Swords of Light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard... what did you set?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be another trap card?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not me that will go to the darkness of hell..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you with your hostility!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.97,0:02:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What you are saying is...\N- It's not a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this darkness, each turn that passes the flame will increase...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four turns left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The so-called "darkness" will be swallowed by a mirror of evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People with weak hearts will be consumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat! Do you know of your situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... draw a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... he's using words to battle with his opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai... is that really his trump card?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the darkness the Player Killer has the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yugi's words are now distracting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem? Can't you even draw a card?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've drawn my ultimate card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear! Supreme King of the Dark Realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately before you play your trump card it will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supreme King of the Dark Realm! Destroy his Curse of Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil Shock Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Card-Hunting Reaper is destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- All right!\N- Yugi, you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?... Damn Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To force me to attack, he used the Hexagram Curse's card
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was prepared even for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity. My monster here is intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll now use my trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Sealing Swords of Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Now we can see the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness was dissipated...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three turns left!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the Sealing Swords of Light, your monsters now for three turns...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are all sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words... your attacks are sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi will attack my monster in the next turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the only card he has on the field is one Curse of Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On my side on the field I have three monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Barox, Dark Chimera, Supreme King of the Dark Realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although the Sealing Swords of Light is in effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the darkness field power source won't disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With only the Curse of Dragon, even if,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}for example, Barox is defeated, it won't change anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn! Hurry and draw a card!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But.. what if...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...he uses a more powerful monster to attack me in the next turn? If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just drew a good card!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Your plan to defeat me in three turns is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Chaos Shield card!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That card puts all your monsters in defense mode...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And increase its defense through an impenetrable shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will use the Castle of Concealing Darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,together with the Chaos Shield, activating a combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is using the castle in the air to make the shield cover
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all his monsters below and increase all of their defense power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.76,0:07:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't your ordinary enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Combo complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With this all of his monsters have more defense points than normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this Chaos Shield, the attack of your monsters are useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still think that you can beat me in three turns?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the darkness was dissipated and we thought that the enemy was down,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he got an amazing defense power...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Player Killer of Darkness fought perfectly protecting himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on the other hand, Yugi-kun has his offensive strategies,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the enemy's defense is too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't just attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there isn't a way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This wouldn't help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This strong defense... how will you break it... Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now.. it's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you have exposed your weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What weakness? Stop saying things that make no sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since this duel started...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been analyzing your strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said in the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you were an incurable coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is now proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already told you! I'm not a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You are really a great coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I AM NOT A COWARD!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you only have two turns left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had already calculated that you would use some kind of shield...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the start...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't joke around! Do you want to feel the fire again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't provoke him anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi is using his words as a weapon to get out of this pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just bluffing and spouting bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a bluff...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't do anything if you're not sure that you are in a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I could imagine that I would be dealing with a coward that hides behind a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Called me coward again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want me to say that... then defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have two turns left...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.41,0:10:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do then? Will you continue? Will you not continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure talk a lot, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.97,0:10:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be toasted to death when this duel is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He escaped that pinch for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the duel starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here! Dark Knight Gaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Do you think that with his attack points you can destroy my fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also I activate my magic card that was set!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.11,0:11:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fusion card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Knight Gaia! Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Knight Gaia?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I end my turn....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this you are finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible! I will lose? In this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dragon Knight Gaia's attack can do {\i0}nothing{\i1} against my Chaos Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that is protecting my monsters against all attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He really {\b0}is{\b1} bluffing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is that smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I can get past the next attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in my turn the Sealing Swords of Light will disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I will deactivate the Chaos Shield and his monsters will be destroyed, with my victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But to be safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My card is Metal Guardian!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put him in defense mode to protect my monster army,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he receives a field source power up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect! My monsters are now 100% protected against any attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it... What a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only thought of how to protect yourself... You're too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the Sealing Swords of Light disappear in the next turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be invincible and will crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are already caught in my trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:13:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you try to protect yourself, the more you can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.87,0:13:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't joke around! I'm warning you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... it's the last turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My card is... Catapult Turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put the Dragon Knight Gaia on the Catapult!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dragon Knight Gaia's attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will increase to 3200 due to the catapult's speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's its strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My monsters are all protected by the Metal Guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I survive this turn, the darkness will once again seal your attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that I would attack your monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.97,0:14:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The defense of the Castle is 3200
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Dragon Knight Gaia's attack is the same 3200,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the battle's damage will be {\i1}nothing{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... let's shoot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Dragon Knight Gaia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Yugi's Life Points have...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used it all in a suicide strategy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bakura! Don't be so calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what will he do if this attack didn't destroy the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... it's still floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you did was talk! What did you mean by "shoot it"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your useless attack did nothing but destroy the floating ring of the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat... You have too much pride of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... I'll put all my monsters in attack mode...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the next turn I'll attack with all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of this duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.65,0:15:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a next turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mysterious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the floating ring was destroyed... why is the castle still floating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sealing Swords of Light caught not only the monsters but the castle as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that castle has been held by the effect of the Sealing Swords of Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this turn ends... what do you think will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is that really it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the effect of the Sealing Swords of Light disappear, the castle will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! My monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless... Due to the Chaos Shield, they can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yugi's victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I.. I lost? Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how the duel ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat! Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is punishment for making fun of me! Fire!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yugi!\N- Yugi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the {\i1}true{\i0} power of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... it's good that you are ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what was that light before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe because of the fire the 3D virtual system had a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... You did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These chips are yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? Take them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.69,0:18:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take these Star chips... I have to leave the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san... you said that, didn't you? That to duel with Yugi was your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man! It won't change anything being here talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want them, then I'll keep them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! That's unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't want them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your pride won't let you fight with these Star chips...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.10,0:19:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can just throw them in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your decision to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.28,0:19:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it was me I wouldn't. Neither the Stars nor the dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then... let's sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As always all you say is shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now.. now..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll borrow these Star chips...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I'm in debt... I don't have the right to fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But.. when I get that right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens... I'll challenge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Who can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Landing a helicopter on the island in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah? Kaiba-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi challenges Kaiba-kun who came to confront Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good way to test the Duel Disks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose, Jounouchi! Show us how much you improved since you got to this island!
